{"tid":1210523,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"認真個句 宜家真係唔會夠做 最起碼做左呢樣野先","createTime":"2019-06-12T13:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T14:17:47.000Z","uid":175427,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"341808611a960bab2eea0d539ebe069294590b40","tid":1210523,"uid":175427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:56:54.000Z","msg":"就係防具<br />\n最基本係每個人都應該有一套類似班狗戴既防毒面具先有得鬥<br />\n今日班狗其實唔洗開槍 靜係放催淚彈已經挽殘我地<br />\n所以只要有副好既防具 佢整幾多催淚彈過黎都可以企係原地繼續防守咁先有得鬥 而唔係俾佢地不停用催淚彈整散人群"},{"pid":"6dd8bef01c4d529bc2716a0f7bbb3c3ea6803a19","tid":1210523,"uid":175427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:57:29.000Z","msg":"有冇人認同"},{"pid":"3f5beac23f59ecd9aa36681e7c51d6472c5c8bc1","tid":1210523,"uid":175427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:57:41.000Z","msg":"認同既推下"},{"pid":"3c276842877b61f34221a074b5645333192d9af6","tid":1210523,"uid":175427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:58:09.000Z","msg":"香港加油"},{"pid":"b5b38f0eba5f9373ac3615e0ce93a53d142649cb","tid":1210523,"uid":175427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:59:30.000Z","msg":"希望今晚唔會有人流血"},{"pid":"bdc594318e0346a9b7d049a55b3a486f1400ac6c","tid":1210523,"uid":175427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:00:56.000Z","msg":"香港加油"},{"pid":"690d606cdbe31c6a2370c745359b02e80863e60b","tid":1210523,"uid":175427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:01:08.000Z","msg":"香港加油"},{"pid":"52fa4ea4d1b3923a649700c8bbc81fa5ce101f01","tid":1210523,"uid":44766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:02:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84a8a4a02435f180a78dae124b4ae1ef763735db","tid":1210523,"uid":175427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:03:35.000Z","msg":"所以如果現場得翻幾百人既話 我真係想佢地撤退 唔好做無謂犧牲"},{"pid":"0731f462bba44344bd6160ae0c77aac5ce8cb280","tid":1210523,"uid":18728